<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink388">
<l>neruppavir kaṉali yuruppucciṉan taṇiyak</l>
<l>karuṅkāl yāttu variniḻa lirīic</l>
<l>ciṟuvarai yiṟappiṟ kāṇkuvai ceṟitoṭip poṉṉēr mēṇi maṭantaiyoṭu</l>
<l>veṉvēl viṭalai muṉṉiya curaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>If you traverse that small mountain, you will see the desert </l>
<l>reached by the warrior with victorious spear and a young girl </l>
<l>with dense bangles and body resembling gold, </l>
<l>[where they] they rest in the striped shade of a black-trunked Yām tree, </l>
<l>waiting for the anger of sun’s heat, burning like fire, to cool down. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
